        "end_idx": 56
      },
      {
        "term": "ease",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 61,
        "end_idx": 65
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Small enough to use on a long flight, Light enough to carry through airports and powerful enough to replace my desktop while on long business trips.",
