      {
        "term": "carry",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 54,
        "end_idx": 59
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Overall, this laptop is definitely a keeper with its simple yet stylish design and its array of fantastic colors to choose from.",
