      },
      {
        "term": "speed",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 18,
        "end_idx": 23
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "You can do it all on this bad boy but the main thing this netbook was desinged for was surfing the web and boy o boy does it ever.",
