        "term": "use",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 59,
        "end_idx": 62
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I previously purchased a 13\" macbook (had pro specs and was aluminum style) which had a nvidia 9800 (If I am not mistaken) and it had major heating issues.",
