      {
        "term": "speed",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 9,
        "end_idx": 14
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The guy then said that if I insist on having the hinge tightened, they can do it for me but I have to accept the condition after the \"repair\".",
