      {
        "term": "warranty",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 101,
        "end_idx": 109
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "No, tey don't even support their own bios and it \"could be a problem with the bios\" How can a company that makes a fairly decent product get away with such insanity??!!",
