      {
        "term": "hard drive",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 45,
        "end_idx": 55
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "No luck, although I waited for hours on the phone-Visited MacHouse, they stated the their call center is down due to too many phonecalls (difficult to believe).",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "call center",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 90,
        "end_idx": 101
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "After having two PC laptops die with in the past 3 years, I was led to the Apple display at Best Buy by the sleek design and promise of less tech issues.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "design",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 114,
        "end_idx": 120
      },
      {
        "term": "tech issues",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 141,
        "end_idx": 152
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "This laptop meets every expectation and Windows 7 is great!",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "Windows 7",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 40,
        "end_idx": 49
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The processor is very quick and effective as I load webpages and applications.",
