        "start_idx": 41,
        "end_idx": 49
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "They sent out the box right away for me to send in my computer, they paid postage and whatnot, but when I got my computer back it still wasn't running right, and now my CD drive wasn't reading anything!",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "CD drive",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 169,
        "end_idx": 177
      },
      {
        "term": "running",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 143,
        "end_idx": 150
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Being a PC user my whole life, it's taking a bit of time to adapt to the OS of a Mac but I'm finding my way around.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "OS",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 73,
        "end_idx": 75
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Not to mention sometimes the whole charger unit will decide not to work entirely.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "charger unit",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 35,
        "end_idx": 47
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The materials that came with the computer did not include the right # anywhere.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "materials",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 4,
        "end_idx": 13
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Upgrading from Windows 7 Starter, thru Windows 7 Home Premium, to Windows 7 Professional was a snap;",
