      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Not to mention it has shit gigs.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "gigs",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 27,
        "end_idx": 31
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The only thing that can be updated is the video, other than that you're all set.",
